  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO ENACT THE BUILDING REGIONAL INFRASTRUCTURE FOR DIVERSE GROWTH IN EDUCATION (BRIDGE) ACT; TO ESTABLISH A UNIFIED STATUTORY FRAMEWORK FOR THE DEVELOPMENT OF REGIONAL SPECIAL PURPOSE SCHOOLS IN MISSISSIPPI; TO CREATE TWO DISTINCT PROGRAMS ADDRESSING SPECIAL-NEEDS STUDENTS AND CAREER AND TECHNICAL EDUCATION AND WORKFORCE TRAINING; TO DIRECT THE MISSISSIPPI DEPARTMENT OF EDUCATION TO CONDUCT STATEWIDE STUDIES, ISSUE GUIDANCE, AND REPORT TO THE LEGISLATURE; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
  },
